Alice Kalimba ni umwari w'umunyarwandakazi wavukiye mu Rwanda akaba ari umukinnyi w'umupira<ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/alice-kalimba</ref>

w'amaguru wikipe yigihugu y'abagore mu [[Rwanda]] ukina nk'umukinnyi wo hagati

== Amateka ==
alice Kalimba yakinnye mu ikipe ya A.S Kigali mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] muri club yabaye kandi mumajonjora yo guhatanira igikombe<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/meet-kalimba-kigali-and-she-amavubis-star-midfielder</ref>

cy'[[Afurika]] muri 2014 akaba kandi ari umwe mu bakinnyi b' abagore bakomeye mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] bagiye bandika amateka mu

mupira w'amaguru mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] no mu Karere<ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/09/kalimba-alice-yasinyiye-ikipe-yo-muri-tanzania/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Alice Kalimba yavutse taliki 11 ugushyingo 1998 avukira mu [[Rwanda]] mu [[Akarere ka Gasabo|Karere ka Gasabo]] mu mujyi wa kigli

abyarwa na se bita Bernard Kalimba na Nyina bita Groliose Ntakirutimana akaba ari umuhererezi mumuryango we

iwabo bavuka ari abana 8 abahungu 4 n'abakobwa 4

== Amashuri yize ==
Alice yize amashuri abanza i [[Kigali]] mu [[Umurenge wa Kacyiru|Murenge wa Kacyiru]] nyuma yaho akomereza amashuri yisumbuye

Iremera Rukoma [[Akarere ka Kamonyi|mukarere ka Kamonyi]] yaje kandi guhindura akomereza mu [[Akarere ka Nyarugenge|karere ka nyarugenge]] mu ishuri

bita solidality academy nyuma kandi yaje gusoreza muru ADB inyarutarama ari naho yakuye impamyabumenyi

y'amashuri yisumbuye akaba yarasoje amasuri yisumbuye mu mwaka wa 2016 gusa kugeza ubu ntago arakomeza [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza.]]

